    "title": "Griffin Lounge: Dance, Dine, and Unwind in Southampton | Griffin",
    "text": "Experience Southampton's Vibrant Lounge & Grill\n\nFeel the Griffin Experience \n\nFood Menu\nEvents\nWelcome to The Griffin Lounge\n\nExperience vibrant dining and dancing at Southampton's premier lounge, bar & grill.\n\nFood Menu\nWhy Griffin?\n\nExperience vibrant nightlife, delicious food, and refreshing drinks at Griffin Lounge & Grill.\n\nGood Food\n\nSensational Music\n\nPool Table\n\nDarts\n\nFunction Room for Hire\n\nWheel Chair Accessibility\n\nGreat Environment\n\nLocation Info\n\nVisit Griffin Lounge, Bar & Grill in Southampton for delicious food, drinks, and vibrant weekend dance events. \n\nAddress\n\n35-37 Anglesea Road Southampton. SO15 5QH\n\nOpening Hours\n\nMondays: 05:00 PM - 11:00 PM\n\nHappy Hour: 05:00 PM - 06:00 PM\n\nTuesdays - Thursdays: 03:00 PM - 11:00 PM\n\nHappy Hour: 03:00 PM - 06:00 PM\n\nFridays - Saturdays: 12:00 PM - 01:30 AM\n\nSundays: 12:00 PM - 11:00 PM\n\nKitchen Closes - 10 PM DAILY\n\nGet in Touch\nYour First Name\nYour Email Address*\nYour Message*\nSubmit Your Inquiry\n\nWe'd love to hear from you! Reach out for inquiries about events, food, and drinks.\n\ninfo@thegriffinlounge.uk\n\n+447404712153\n\nEnter your email address here\nJoin our weekend events now\n\n© 2024. All rights reserved.\n\nThe Griffin Lounge\n\nBar and Grill",
